HoneySat Artifact Licensing Notice 
==================================

This archive mixes HoneySat-authored material with third-party
software.

HoneySat-authored content in this archive (including deployment and
evaluation documentation, Docker compose files, honeysat-webpage-v2
assets, telnet-honeypot code, and other infrastructure not listed
under "Third-party components" below) is provided under the MIT
License, unless a different license header is present in a specific
file. The full text of the MIT License is included at the end of
this document. The MIT terms do not override the licenses of bundled
third-party components.

Third-party components and licenses 
-----------------------------------

The following components are used by HoneySat. Some are included in
this archive for the convenience of artifact evaluation. Others are
downloaded from their original repositories during deployment. These
components retain their own licenses as set by their authors.

- YAMCS

  - Location in this archive: `deployment/projects/yamcs/` - License:
    GNU Affero General Public License v3.0 (AGPL-3.0) - License file
    in this archive: `deployment/projects/yamcs/yamcs/AGPL-LICENSE.txt`
  - Upstream repository: https://github.com/yamcs/yamcs

- RACCOON OS userspace and wrapper

  - Location in this archive: `deployment/projects/raccoon-wrapper/`
  - License: GNU General Public License v3.0 (GPL-3.0) - License file
    in this archive: `deployment/projects/raccoon-wrapper/LICENSE` -
    Upstream repository and license:
    https://gitlab.com/rccn/raccoon-os/-/blob/master/LICENSE

- SUCHAI flight software and ground station

  - Locations in this archive:
    `deployment/projects/honeysat-suchai-fsw/`,
    `deployment/projects/honeysat-suchai-gs/`, and related Docker
    configurations
  - License: GNU General Public License v3.0 (GPL-3.0) - Source is
    fetched during Docker builds from:
    https://gitlab.com/spel-uchile/suchai-2-software
  - Any images built from these Dockerfiles include GPL-licensed code
    and must be redistributed under GPLv3 with corresponding source.
    For the upstream license text see:
    https://gitlab.com/spel-uchile/suchai-flight-software/-/blob/feature/framework/LICENSE

- HoneySat API

  - Location in this archive: `deployment/projects/honeysat-api/`
  - License: MIT License - License file in this archive:
    `deployment/projects/honeysat-api/LICENSE`

Use notes 
---------

- This archive redistributes YAMCS (AGPL-3.0) and RACCOON (GPL-3.0)
  source.
  Use, modification, and redistribution of these components must comply
  with their respective licenses, including any copyleft requirements.
- SUCHAI components are incorporated via Docker images built from
  GPL-licensed source, and redistribution of those images must also
  comply with GPLv3.  
- Components are typically run in separate
  containers and are provided as an aggregation of independently
  licensed works.
- This summary is for convenience only and does not
  replace the actual license texts.

